Name: Shining Jump Jump
About the game: Jump! Jump! Jump! Yggdra Resonanc (old Shining Maiden)'s cute girl jumping game~! - Use the left and right keys to go up the stairs, and if you climb a place other than the stairs, you will fall as it is! - There is no time to worry in front of a fork in the road, a fierce monster chasing you! - Every time you climb the stairs, you get various rewards and acquire beautiful girls! - Climb high and break the best record.
